<i>â™ª Big adventure! </i>
<i>â™ª Tons of fun </i>

01:00.761 --> 01:03.095
<i>â™ª A beautiful heart!  </i>
<i>â™ª Faithful and strong! </i>

01:03.097 --> 01:05.397
<i>â™ª Sharing kindness </i>
<i>â™ª it's an easy feat </i>

01:05.399 --> 01:07.433
<i>â™ª And magic makes it</i>
<i>all complete! â™ª</i>

01:07.435 --> 01:09.468
<i>â™ª To have my little pony </i>

